            %i Sami Haile, Delaware  |  Groomsmen
            %p I knew Sami since I was four and a half years old.  We grew up together and went to St. Joseph school.  We saw each other daily until I left for the US. Despite the distance we kept in touch. When I told Sammy I had met the “one” he was beyond excited for me. I can honestly say Sami is more than my best friend. He is more like my brother.
          %hr
