            %i  Mehari Zewdu, Addis Ababa  |  Groomsmen
            %p Mehari and I have been friends for many years. We met when I returned to Addis from the U.S. I can say we have had some great memories together.  Mehari is fun to be around and has a great sense of humor. When I met Samra and introduced her to my friends Mehari was the first to meet her at a BBQ at his place. I am glad to have him be part of our special day.
          %hr
