            %i Abrahm Tesfa Kiros, Addis Ababa  |  Groomsmen
            %p Abrish is my cousin and we grew up together. Even at a young age I have always known I can rely on him for great advice and moral support. He’s always positive, generous, and thoughtful. Abrish is very smart and motivated and I am always inspired when I am around him. He’s always laughing and enjoying life to the fullest. When he met Samra early on in our relationship he was very excited for me and always encouraged me to take the next step. 
          %hr
